  "text": "It is worth emphasizing here that the dose-response relationship of DTC to 131 I treatment has been much less thoroughly analyzed than that of other cancers to Endocrine-Related Cancer (2005) 12 773-803 www.endocrinology-journals.org external beam therapy (Suwinski & GawkowskaSuwinska 2001) . Also, the dose rate in radioiodine therapy deserves much more attention, because at <0.6 Gy/h, more and more sublethal cell damage may be repaired [CITATION_1] .",
